    / _ \|  _ \|  \/  |_   _|
   / /_\ \ | | | .  . | | |  
   |  _  | | | | |\/| | | |  
   | | | | |/ /| |  | |_| |_ 
   \_| |_/___/ \_|  |_/\___/ 
                               
    DELTA MOBILE FLY v2.0
    Server-Side | Real Physics | Anti-Detection
    Commands: /fly, /stop, /target [name], /fling [name], /speed [number]
    ]])
end

--// EXECUTE
Init()

